1. Moj *šef* je otišao na sastanak. (My *boss* went to a meeting.)
2. *Šefu* treba poslati izvještaj do kraja dana. (The *boss* needs to receive the report by the end of the day.)
3. *Šefica* je vrlo zahtjevna, ali jako dobra u svom poslu. (The *female boss* is very demanding, but very good at her job.)
4. Molim vas, *šefe*, možete li mi dati nekoliko dana odmora? (Please, *boss*, can you give me a few days off?)
5. *Šefov* automobil je veoma skup. (The *boss's* car is very expensive.)
6. Uvijek se držim *šefovih* uputa. (I always follow the *boss's* instructions.)
7. Vidjela sam *šefa* u gradu jučer. (I saw the *boss* in the city yesterday.)
8. Ova odluka će biti donesena od strane *šefova* tima. (This decision will be made by the *boss's* team.)